1. Định nghĩa vấn đề (Define Problem)¶

  • M t:
    • B d liu bao gm 50 mu t mi loi trong s ba loi Iris (Iris setosa, Iris virginica v Iris versicolor).
    • Bn c im c o t mi mu: chiu di v chiu rng ca cc l i(sepal) v cnh hoa (petal), tnh bng cm.
  • D liu vo:
    • sepal length (cm)
    • sepal width (cm)
    • petal length (cm)
    • petal width (cm)
  • Kt qu: class (Iris Setosa, Iris Versicolour, Iris Virginica)

Chuẩn hóa dữ liệu (Data Normalize)¶

Chun ha cc tnh cht a v cng mt min tr

  • Min-Max Normalization $$ z = \frac{x - min(x)}{max(x) - min(x)} $$
  • Standard Normalization $$ z = \frac{x - \mu}{\sigma} $$

Lu : Qu trnh chun ha c th lm trong phn thc nghim thut ton

Min-Max Normalization¶
